    <div>
        <h3>Woadic Chief OTK</h3>
        <p>The strategy of this deck is to combine <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="52">Woadic Chief</a> with many cheap 0 cost spells to try to reach 25 damage in the first turn.</p>

        <h5>Tips for play:</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>You can use <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="108">Unempty Coffin</a> to discount the cost on <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="52">Woadic Chief</a></li>
            <li><a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="380">Scorching Serve</a> removes creatures in opposing lands if necessary</li>
            <li>An alternative win-condition is using <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="432">Blue Slimey</a> to remove a creature in the opposing land and using <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="154">Subliminal Strength</a> to raise the damage</li>
            <li><a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="89">Red Eyeling</a> can recur 0 cost spells to help further dig and increase <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="52">Woadic Chiefs</a> damage</li>
            <li>The chosen Hero <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="317">Grand Prix</a> allows you to gain more benefits from Slimeys, Red Eyeling, and <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="441">Djini Ghost</a> floops!</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

