    <div>
        <h3>Off-Meta Party God Lane Shift</h3>
        <p>The strategy of this deck is to move creatures across your empty lanes to accrue big damage.</p>

        <h5>Tips for play:</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>Each creature has benefits to changing lanes. Payoffs like <a asp-page="/Card" asp-route-id="62">Woad Blood</a> can push through big damage or KO opposing creatures.</li>
            <li>Keep a lane open to move creatures on, if your opponent tries to block your damage, shift to that lane and use your pump spells to push more damage.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

